        <h3 class="node-title article__title--card">
            <a href="/news/daedalus-humanitarian-health-violent-conflicts" rel="bookmark"><span class='field-wrapper article__title article__title--card'>New Dædalus on Delivering Humanitarian Health Services in Violent Conflicts</span></a>
        </h3>
        <div class="article__teaser article__teaser--card field field-node--field-teaser-plain field-name-field-teaser-plain field-type-string-long field-label-hidden">
    <div class="field-items">
          <div class="field-item">The Spring 2023 issue of Dædalus on “Delivering Humanitarian Health Services in Violent Conflicts” features essays, poetry, fiction, and visual art to illuminate the dilemmas facing humanitarian health actors and the potential for innovation in humanitarian health delivery.</div>
