        <h3 class="node-title card-project__title">
            <a href="/project/promoting-dialogue-arms-control-disarmament" rel="bookmark"><span class="project__title project__title--card">Promoting Dialogue on Arms Control and Disarmament</span>
</a>
        </h3>
        <div class="project__teaser project__teaser--card field field-node--field-teaser field-name-field-teaser field-type-text-long field-label-hidden">
    <div class="field-items">
          <div class="field-item"><p>Through Track-2 meetings between U.S., Russian, and Chinese experts, <em>Promoting Dialogue on Arms Control and Disarmament</em> seeks to identify a range of measures to enhance strategic stability among the major nuclear powers and avoid costly arms races.</p>
</div>
      </div>
</div>

                    <div class="field field-node--field-chairs card-project__people">
                <div class="field-label">Chair</div>
                <div class="field-items">Steven E. Miller</div>
