        <h3 class="node-title card-project__title">
            <a href="/project/reconsidering-rules-space" rel="bookmark"><span class="project__title project__title--card">Reconsidering the Rules of Space</span>
</a>
        </h3>
        <div class="project__teaser project__teaser--card field field-node--field-teaser field-name-field-teaser field-type-text-long field-label-hidden">
    <div class="field-items">
          <div class="field-item"><p>This study examined the global security implications of expanding commercial and military uses of space, and considered international rules and principles needed to maintain a balanced use of space over the long term.</p>
</div>
      </div>
