        <h3 class="node-title card-project__title">
            <a href="/project/us-policy-toward-russia" rel="bookmark"><span class="project__title project__title--card">U.S. Policy Toward Russia</span>
</a>
        </h3>
        <div class="project__teaser project__teaser--card field field-node--field-teaser field-name-field-teaser field-type-text-long field-label-hidden">
    <div class="field-items">
          <div class="field-item"><p>The Academy conducted a major reexamination of U.S. foreign policy toward Russia. The goal was to develop a comprehensive, coherent, and effective policy on U.S.-Russian relations for consideration by the then new U.S. administration, Congress, and the media.</p>
</div>
      </div>
</div>

