        <h3 class="node-title card-project__title">
            <a href="/project/new-dilemmas-ethics-technology-and-war" rel="bookmark"><span class="project__title project__title--card">New Dilemmas in Ethics, Technology, and War</span>
</a>
        </h3>
        <div class="project__teaser project__teaser--card field field-node--field-teaser field-name-field-teaser field-type-text-long field-label-hidden">
    <div class="field-items">
          <div class="field-item"><p><em>New Dilemmas in Ethics, Technology and War</em>&nbsp;is a three-year study exploring the intricate, rapidly evolving relationship between advancements in military technology and the moral and ethical dilemmas that new technologies pose for states, international organizations, and global society.&nbsp;</p>
</div>
      </div>
</div>

