                                    </div>
        <h3 class="node-title article-teaser__title">
            <a href="/news/next-generation-nuclear-expertise" rel="bookmark"><span class='field-wrapper article__title article__title--teaser'>Early- and Mid-Career Experts Reflect on New Nuclear Book</span></a>
        </h3>
        <div class="article-teaser__body">
            <div class="article__teaser article__teaser--teaser field field-node--field-teaser-plain field-name-field-teaser-plain field-type-string-long field-label-hidden">
    <div class="field-items">
          <div class="field-item">How do younger scholars think about new nuclear challenges? The Project on Nuclear Issues at the Center for Strategic and International Studies invited early- and mid-career experts to share their thoughts on the Academy publication The Fragile Balance of Terror. </div>
      </div>
</div>

        </div>
        
    </div>

</article>
</div>
          <div class="field-item"><article  class="article-teaser clearfix">

