        <h3 class="node-title article-teaser__title">
            <a href="/news/book-launch-csis-fragile-balance-terror-deterrence-nuclear-age" rel="bookmark"><span class='field-wrapper article__title article__title--teaser'>Book Launch with CSIS for The Fragile Balance of Terror: Deterrence in the Nuclear Age</span></a>
        </h3>
        <div class="article-teaser__body">
            <div class="article__teaser article__teaser--teaser field field-node--field-teaser-plain field-name-field-teaser-plain field-type-string-long field-label-hidden">
    <div class="field-items">
          <div class="field-item">The Academy and the Center for Strategic and International Studies launched a new book -- The Fragile Balance of Terror: Deterrence in the Nuclear Age -- at a cohosted event in Washington D.C. featuring one of the volume&#039;s editors and multiple authors. </div>
      </div>
